messages.message: When I run a Build project in the legacy flow UI, extra whitespace shows up in the extractions. It only shows up in Flow Review, not in Build, and not even in the Refiner. I tried adding a clean function to fix this in Build (it does a `re.sub("\s+", " ", x)` ), but this had no effect.
what environment is this? can you share a link to the flow review page?
probably has to do with how we render things with markdown, which eats spaces
